1. WAP to accept a string and count the number of words in it.
2. WAP to accept a string and count the number of 'a' in it.
3. WAP to accept a string and count the number of vowels in it.
4. WAP to accept full name of a persone and display his initials.
	Eg. Manish Kumar Mishra	=	MKM
5. WAP to accept a string and find whether it is a pallindrome
   or not.
   Eg. madam is a pallindrome
